What is amfPHP ?

Amfphp is the easiest way to connect a client to a server. It gives a common language to client and server side applications by using objects. It is the most straightforward remoting solution for php, the most efficient, the most mature and it is free.

Of course it is also the most popular !
New leadership for amfPHP

Silex Labs has taken leadership of the amfphp project, and has set up teams for development and documentation. The goals are to federate the community, and to promote new ideas and new projects related to amfphp.
